WEBVTT

00:00.531 --> 00:01.769
Previously on Z Nation.

00:01.869 --> 00:04.137
A bullet to the heart will reveal the truth.

00:04.238 --> 00:05.872
No!

00:09.777 --> 00:11.445
I love you.

00:11.479 --> 00:12.479
I love you too.

00:13.247 --> 00:14.147
Warren, we have to go.

00:14.182 --> 00:15.148
No! We have to go now.

00:15.183 --> 00:17.083
We can't let him turn.

00:17.118 --> 00:18.952
We have to give him mercy!

